OL,3,CMasked gunman fires shot at house in
OL,4,CNewtownards
OL,6,FA masked gunman has fired a shot at a
OL,7,Fhouse in Newtownards, police have said.
OL,9,FNo injuries were reported following
OL,10,Fthe incident in the Half Acre Lane
OL,11,Farea on Tuesday night.
OL,13,FThe PSNI said a masked man dressed in
OL,14,Fblack was seen fleeing the scene
OL,15,Ftowards Church Street.
OL,17,F"Police received a report at around
OL,18,F11.26pm of a broken window at a
OL,19,Fproperty in the Half Acre Lane area,"
OL,20,Fthey said.
OL,26,@yD@AOU{D@eO]
