OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781767088
OL,3,CMasked gunman fires shot at house in
OL,4,CNewtownards
OL,6,F"Officers attended the address, where
OL,7,Fthe damage was subsequently deemed to
OL,8,Fhave been caused by a gunshot.
OL,10,F"It is believed this was fired just a
OL,11,Ffew minutes before the report was made
OL,12,Fto police, between 11.15pm and 11.20pm.
OL,14,F"One person was in the house at the
OL,15,Ftime.
OL,17,F"However, no injuries were reported.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUyD@AOU
