OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1781767088
OL,3,CMasked gunman fires shot at house in
OL,4,CNewtownards
OL,6,F"It was further reported that a masked
OL,7,Fman, dressed in black, was seen in the
OL,8,Farea holding what appeared to be a
OL,9,Fsmall handgun, before making off
OL,10,Ftowards Church Street.
OL,12,F"Inquiries are ongoing and we would
OL,13,Fappeal to anyone who was in the area
OL,14,Fat the time or who has any
OL,15,Finformation, including dash-cam, CCTV
OL,16,For other footage, to contact police on
OL,17,F101, quoting reference number 1891 of
OL,18,F16/06/26."
OL,20,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
